Name: SNOMED_CT
Title: SNOMED CT (all versions)
Descriptino: SNOMED CT is the most comprehensive and precise clinical health terminology product in the world, owned and distributed around the world by The International Health Terminology Standards Development Organisation (IHTSDO).

Name: PHOccupationalDataForHealthODH
Title: Occupational Data for Health (ODH)
Descriptino: The concepts representing the values supporting Occupational Data for Health, including Job Supervisory Level or Pay Grade (ODH) code system consists of data elements that describe a person's work information, structured to facilitate individual, population, and public health use; not intended to support billing.).

Name: ObservationReferenceRangeMeaningCodes
Title: Observation Reference Range Meaning Codes
Descriptino: This value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the meaning/use of a reference range for a particular target population.

Name: ObservationValue
Title: ObservationValue
Descriptino: This code system covers all concepts of HL7-defined values for the Observation value element, when it has a coded datatype.

Name: WorkClassificationODH
Title: Work Classification (Occupational Data for Health)
Descriptino: Code system of concepts representing a person's job type as defined by compensation and sector (e.g. paid vs. unpaid, self-employed vs. not self-employed, government vs. private, etc.).
